Create a CallableStatementSpy (JDBC 4 version) to spy upon a CallableStatement.

Parameters:
sql - The SQL used for this CallableStatement
connectionSpy - The ConnectionSpy which produced this CallableStatementSpy
realCallableStatement - The real CallableStatement that is being spied upon
